      <title>淡水河谷铁矿石产量超出矿山业绩预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/vale-s-iron-ore-output-tops-estimates-on-mine-performance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西矿业巨头淡水河谷公司第一季度铁矿石产量超出预期，运营业绩改善，第三方采购量增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/vale-s-iron-ore-output-tops-estimates-on-mine-performance</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 21:43:42 GMT</pubDate>
