    <item>
      <title>加拿大提高资本利得税以使住房更便宜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/canada-raising-capital-gains-taxes-to-pay-for-housing-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大将提高企业和富人的资本利得税，以帮助支付数百亿美元的新支出，这些支出旨在使住房更加负担得起并改善年轻人的生活。 BNN Bloomberg 的 Jon Erlichman 报道“彭博市场：收盘”。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/canada-raising-capital-gains-taxes-to-pay-for-housing-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 21:16:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SEC 针对自己员工的短信行为，禁止在工作电话上使用 WhatsApp</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/sec-targets-its-own-staff-s-texting-nixes-whatsapp-on-agency-s-mobile-phones</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国证券交易委员会已屏蔽员工工作手机上的第三方消息应用程序和短信，使其自己的做法更接近其为行业执行的标准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/sec-targets-its-own-staff-s-texting-nixes-whatsapp-on-agency-s-mobile-phones</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 20:01:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大提高资本利得税，为住房筹集数十亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/canada-hikes-capital-gains-tax-to-raise-billions-for-housing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大将提高企业和富人的资本利得税，以帮助支付数百亿美元的新支出，这些支出旨在使住房更加负担得起并改善年轻人的生活。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/canada-hikes-capital-gains-tax-to-raise-billions-for-housing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 20:01:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织改变规则以加速债务重组，避免中国拖延</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/imf-board-changes-lending-rules-to-speed-up-debt-restructuring</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织(IMF)改变了支持那些陷入债务重组困境的国家的程序，此举旨在避免近期广泛归咎于中国的拖延。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/imf-board-changes-lending-rules-to-speed-up-debt-restructuring</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 18:07:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>毛伊岛消防官员为拉海纳致命大火的反应辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/hawaiian-electric-hits-40-year-low-ahead-of-maui-fire-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[毛伊岛消防局官员为他们对夏威夷历史上最致命的火灾的初步反应进行了辩护，称他们一直留在 8 月 8 日大火的现场，直到大火被完全扑灭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/hawaiian-electric-hits-40-year-low-ahead-of-maui-fire-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 17:18:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟报告支持电信整合和强劲的能源市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/eu-report-calls-for-telecom-consolidation-strong-energy-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据欧盟委托编写的一份关于竞争力的报告，欧盟应考虑对电信运营商进行整合，以此作为改善欧盟移动和固定网络的一种方式，并应进一步整合其能源市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/eu-report-calls-for-telecom-consolidation-strong-energy-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 16:24:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国放松对人民币的控制使货币能够测试一个关键的里程碑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/china-s-fixing-surprise-paves-way-for-yuan-to-test-key-7-3-level</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国在一个月内第二次尝试放松对人民币的管制，为人民币测试自去年11月以来从未出现过的心理里程碑打开了大门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/china-s-fixing-surprise-paves-way-for-yuan-to-test-key-7-3-level</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 10:08:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元复苏、收益率上升导致新兴市场货币跌至 2024 年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/emerging-market-assets-sink-to-2024-low-amid-growth-rate-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔暗示利率可能会在更长时间内保持高位，导致美国国债收益率飙升，并进一步恶化全球市场情绪，发展中国家货币下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/emerging-market-assets-sink-to-2024-low-amid-growth-rate-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 08:18:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
